metadata.description:
properties panel is the game board.



As a reborn person, the King knows all about the properties panel.



The FIVE BASIC ATTRIBUTES ARE IMPORTANT: STRENGTH AFFECTS PHYSICAL ATTACKS, AGILITY AFFECTS MOVEMENT SPEED AND ATTACK SPEED, SPIRIT AFFECTS MAGIC DAMAGE AND MANA, CONSTITUTION IS RELATED TO HEALTH, AND ENDURANCE IS RELATED TO DEFENSE.



As for critical strikes, they require equipment or a title.
